snippet.title: Old Man's Journey Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Old Man's Journey is a soul-searching puzzle adventure about life, loss and hope. It's out now for iOS, Android and Steam!
App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/old-mans-journey/id1204902987
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=es.brokenrul.oldmansjourney
Windos & Mac:
http://oldmansjourney.com
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/581270/Old_Mans_Journey/
Humble:
https://www.humblebundle.com/store/old-mans-journey

Music by SCNTFC - http://scntfc.com/
Editing by Salon Alpin - http://salonalpin.tv
